  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate safety and tolerability of PF-00299804 in Japanese patients with advanced
      malignant solid tumors at doses up to the clinically recommended phase 2 dose in non-Japanese
      studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
